34:24.603 --> 34:27.273
I get 'em. Everyone gets 'em.

34:27.357 --> 34:28.524
You kill a lot of people?

34:30.610 --> 34:32.902
- What?
- In Iraq.

34:33.321 --> 34:35.531
Is it any different than killing folk over here?

34:35.614 --> 34:36.866
Now, what do you mean by that, Johnny?

34:36.992 --> 34:38.659
Is it different than killing white folk?

34:38.994 --> 34:40.119
No.

34:40.454 --> 34:41.620
Innocents.

34:42.038 --> 34:43.121
You know...

34:43.998 --> 34:46.500
Civilians, kids, that sort of thing.

34:46.835 --> 34:48.210
You see their faces in your dreams?

34:48.670 --> 34:50.670
I hear a lot of veterans have that problem.

34:50.922 --> 34:54.175
You need to check your fridge, Johnny.
This beer's warm as piss.

34:56.386 --> 34:58.012
You see Ellen May's face?

35:03.852 --> 35:05.352
No, I haven't.

35:07.105 --> 35:09.023
No, you wouldn't since

35:10.567 --> 35:12.610
she wasn't exactly innocent.

35:16.948 --> 35:21.243
Boyd, do you know
about the EPA Superfund?

35:21.536 --> 35:26.874
They come in after
there's a big environmental disaster like, say,

35:26.958 --> 35:29.668
a slurry pond breaks its banks.

35:29.753 --> 35:33.297
Pour in a king's ransom
of government funds for the cleanup.

35:33.590 --> 35:34.882
Well, let me guess.

35:35.884 --> 35:38.427
You want Frank Browning
to bust open one of his ponds

35:38.553 --> 35:42.181
so all of you can suck off the federal tit,

35:42.265 --> 35:44.058
but he ain't willing to play along.

35:44.643 --> 35:45.976
Told you he was sharp.

35:47.729 --> 35:50.648
Frank Browning is indeed a problem.

35:50.816 --> 35:52.817
You seem like a problem solver.

35:53.401 --> 35:54.902
You want me to twist his arm?

35:55.487 --> 35:56.570
We'd prefer it

35:57.322 --> 35:58.948
if you kill him.

36:07.999 --> 36:09.458
And if I say no?

36:09.584 --> 36:11.585
After all we've given you?

36:12.754 --> 36:13.921
Come again?

36:15.465 --> 36:16.632
How about the whorehouse?

36:18.426 --> 36:19.510
Drug running.

36:19.928 --> 36:21.679
You ever think how you have that?

36:23.765 --> 36:24.932
'Cause we let you.

36:25.100 --> 36:28.435
Keeps your cross-eyed
brethren down the mountain placated.

36:28.520 --> 36:30.271
You know what that word means,
"placated"?

36:30.605 --> 36:32.022
Yes, I do.

36:33.775 --> 36:36.277
But I think the word
you're looking for is "pacified."

36:37.529 --> 36:39.446
I think you're missing the point.

36:39.823 --> 36:41.740
Your daddy got the point.

36:42.951 --> 36:45.327
Crowders do what we say.

36:45.620 --> 36:49.290
And to be crystal goddamn

36:50.250 --> 36:51.584
clear,

36:52.627 --> 36:55.754
kill Frank Browning, or we'll destroy you.

37:03.930 --> 37:06.807
Wow. I was not expecting this.

37:07.601 --> 37:10.185
When the Marshals do things,
we try to do it right.

37:11.313 --> 37:12.479
I like how you do things.

37:12.606 --> 37:15.316
I know I give you a charge,
but you seem almost giddy.

37:15.442 --> 37:17.693
That got anything to do
with what's in the bag?

37:17.819 --> 37:18.861
My school books?

37:18.987 --> 37:20.112
Jackie.

37:20.989 --> 37:23.282
I figured out why Jody
came back to Lexington

37:23.366 --> 37:24.950
instead of just taking off.

37:25.035 --> 37:27.161
Wasn't 'cause of the kids or Katrina.

37:27.829 --> 37:31.457
It was for the money,
and I'm pretty sure it is in that bag.

37:33.668 --> 37:35.044
What are you gonna do about it?

37:35.170 --> 37:38.047
It's ill-gotten gains.
If I find it, I got to turn it in.

37:38.840 --> 37:39.965
But...

37:40.050 --> 37:41.675
If it was never found

37:41.801 --> 37:44.136
and it made its way back
to Katrina and the kids,

37:45.013 --> 37:47.014
that wouldn't be such a bad thing.

37:54.481 --> 37:55.814
What's up, chief?

37:55.899 --> 37:59.860
So, were you gonna tell me what
happened or just keep it to yourself?

38:00.070 --> 38:01.528
I didn't want to wake you.

38:01.821 --> 38:03.072
That's very thoughtful.

38:03.657 --> 38:06.325
Let me guess. In all this,
you still haven't made it to Tramble.

38:06.409 --> 38:08.327
First thing tomorrow morning.

38:08.703 --> 38:10.162
- Where are you?
- Don't worry.

38:10.246 --> 38:11.664
We ain't paying for the room.

38:12.082 --> 38:13.832
What, is she sitting right beside you?

38:14.542 --> 38:15.668
I hear the shower running.

38:15.752 --> 38:17.252
Probably just gonna sleep on the couch.

38:17.379 --> 38:19.213
That'd be a first for you, wouldn't it?

38:20.215 --> 38:21.674
She in love with you yet?

38:22.092 --> 38:26.637
Art, this girl ain't the least bit
interested in an old fart like me.

38:26.721 --> 38:28.555
He said humbly.

38:28.890 --> 38:30.015
Tell me we're done.

38:30.100 --> 38:31.517
We're done. For now.

38:31.768 --> 38:32.851
Go see your fath...

38:58.003 --> 38:59.378
The hell is that?

38:59.587 --> 39:02.172
FBI folder stuffed full of take-out menus.

39:03.049 --> 39:05.426
I was gonna tell you
your time was running out.

39:05.552 --> 39:08.345
They gave us everything we needed
to short-circuit your deal.

39:08.430 --> 39:10.514
But you cannot tell a lie.

39:10.890 --> 39:12.599
Didn't I teach you anything?

39:12.892 --> 39:14.268
Not really.

39:15.603 --> 39:18.522
Look, I know you think
you're the toughest man

39:18.606 --> 39:21.608
that God ever strung a gut through,
and you got your plan.

39:21.693 --> 39:23.944
Long as you stick to it,
everything's gonna work out,

39:24.029 --> 39:26.613
but just 'cause you got a plan
don't mean it's a good one.

39:26.781 --> 39:28.699
Killed a guy last night didn't understand that.

39:28.783 --> 39:30.451
Am I supposed to be impressed?

39:30.535 --> 39:31.952
It's just a fact.

39:32.454 --> 39:37.041
My plan, Arlo, was to see that
under no circumstances you got a deal.

39:37.125 --> 39:39.626
Well, I'm gonna change that.
I'm gonna cut you a deal right now.

39:39.753 --> 39:41.128
You must be hard up, boy.

39:41.212 --> 39:43.922
Suffice to say,
there's something in it for both of us.

39:44.257 --> 39:45.549
Go on.

39:47.302 --> 39:50.804
We know Drew's alive and in Harlan,
but it's gonna be a bitch to find him.

39:50.930 --> 39:53.057
- We could use your help.
- Now we're getting to it.

39:53.141 --> 39:56.060
What you don't realise is,
you could use our help.

39:56.895 --> 39:58.812
Theo Tonin knows Drew's alive, too,

39:58.938 --> 40:01.648
and guess who he's got
on his payroll helping him look for him?

40:01.900 --> 40:04.068
- Boyd Crowder.
- You're bullshitting me.

40:04.152 --> 40:06.153
Son you never had is working against you.

40:06.279 --> 40:08.238
So, maybe I did teach you
something after all.

40:08.323 --> 40:11.075
If they find him first, your deal evaporates,

40:11.159 --> 40:14.244
but you tell me right now and we get to him,

40:14.829 --> 40:18.916
I will make sure you
live out your days in a country-club jail.

40:19.000 --> 40:20.250
Let me consider it.

40:20.418 --> 40:22.503
For once in our lives, let's work together?

40:22.587 --> 40:24.129
I've considered it.

40:25.006 --> 40:26.548
Eat shit.

40:33.348 --> 40:34.681
So be it.

40:36.101 --> 40:37.976
I'm gonna go see Sheriff Hunter now.

40:38.061 --> 40:39.645
Josiah says he knows Drew.

40:39.729 --> 40:42.689
Maybe he'll take that
country-club deal instead of you?

40:44.234 --> 40:47.361
See what you did there? I struck a nerve.

40:47.445 --> 40:49.238
- Didn't do anything.
- Exactly.

40:49.364 --> 40:53.450
As long as I can remember, whenever you got
bad news, you had a face like a statue.

40:53.785 --> 40:55.077
Can't help I'm good-looking.

40:55.161 --> 40:56.870
So long, Arlo.

40:57.872 --> 41:02.126
You're gonna die here
and not in the distant future.

41:02.210 --> 41:05.129
Tomorrow or maybe Sunday after chow.

41:05.213 --> 41:06.380
You threatening me?

41:06.464 --> 41:07.673
And I'll tell you something.

41:07.924 --> 41:10.473
I'm gonna be glad when I hear the news.
